{"tid":1045641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來９０年代黎香港玩既日本人多過依家好多！","createTime":"2019-03-03T17:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T07:06:06.000Z","uid":41375,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d540388a6b424d5defef0d404749f888f1974fd8","tid":1045641,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"出面睇到post話近排香港Ｄ日本人多左，但原來廿年前既香港仲多日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淪陷前夕(1996年)，來至日本既訪港旅客一年間有近240萬人次，係最大既遊客來源地，佔香港整體旅客比例約20%<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/010132_8c0c9f3d5906abbff2c75129dff45e6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F010132_8c0c9f3d5906abbff2c75129dff45e6d.png&h=04d7cbbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但2017年黎香港既日本人都係得123萬人次<br />\n到底幾時先會回復返９０年代中既水位，出街見到周圍都係來至北方既醜陋面孔就好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B70001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB70001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=e2027004\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B70001FD2000XXXXB0100.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/%E5%A4%8F%E6%B0%B4%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%9C%E6%A5%AD/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%A2%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC-a0cd5ef7dc80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25AD%2597%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%25A5%25AD%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A2%259E%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC-a0cd5ef7dc80&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=8866f867\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/%E5%A4%8F%E6%B0%B4%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%9C%E6%A5%AD/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%A2%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC-a0cd5ef7dc80</a>"},{"pid":"57e77805bf01e9c4e4974164789bad2389797b9d","tid":1045641,"uid":3936,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"係日本讀書+做野<br />\n如果同中年日本人傾話黎自香港<br />\n佢地好多都會話黎過香港玩<br />\n不過係20年以上"},{"pid":"9d31ffba2eee495bf550117e0fac6e3715d43782","tid":1045641,"uid":160348,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"96年多咗係嚟探香港最後一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d4a455c19316881b413a1456858d7c7544134e","tid":1045641,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"去大陸玩平咁多<br />\n都係中國地方，點會黎香港"},{"pid":"bc99021af12f36f8f1eed70dff8b5fc2df848467","tid":1045641,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:21:44.000Z","msg":"好記得90年代嗰時<br />\n尖沙咀成日見到一架架髹紅色寫住「名鉄観光」嘅旅遊巴"},{"pid":"43d11228f9a6c56d41734b3782f7a46b6931d45a","tid":1045641,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6aba31c820732448320309d3af2312ae68ba4dd","tid":1045641,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"而家去泰國同星洲都唔黎香港LA."},{"pid":"6a07479527a2acd5107f988af9adf32ffe075789","tid":1045641,"uid":179192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"成街都係日本/韓國食物 我飛韓國/係返日本食唔好？"},{"pid":"d9d94247f696c9b37f0649c18a3882f0774acfe7","tid":1045641,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"仲好好劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賣金飾賣俾佢哋賣貴好多"},{"pid"